message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which has been designed to meet your specific needs. Given its value and the benefits it offers, I believe we can come to an agreement that's mutually beneficial. Considering the product's worth to you, I propose a price of $9,500. This allows us both to feel satisfied with the transaction. If this proposal meets your expectations, please let me know so we can proceed. Thank you for considering our offer.
